name: SystemDependency
desc: An object that specifies the update order between multiple systems.

items.desc: An update order that requests RealityKit update this system before it updates another specified system.

items.name: case after(System.Type)
items.desc: An update order that requests RealityKit update this system after it updates another specified system.
